#

One-Pot Beef Stew

135 min
$20
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasyOne-Pot

Description

A hearty and comforting dish that combines tender beef, fresh vegetables, and aromatic herbs all cooked together in one pot for easy cleanup.

Ingredients

  • beef chuck, cubed: 2 pounds
  • carrots, chopped: 3
  • potatoes, diced: 4
  • onion, chopped: 1
  • garlic, minced: 3 cloves
  • beef broth: 4 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • thyme, dried: 1 teaspoon
  • bay leaves: 2
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
